{"tid":1027852,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"4男女港珠澳大橋上停車野餐拍照 還丟垃圾落海","createTime":"2019-02-19T05:36:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-19T11:30:40.000Z","uid":75969,"like":165,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"52b677d4d923b47834e9b48de2903113a98cabfb","tid":1027852,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T05:36:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190219/_2019021912522940972.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190219%2F_2019021912522940972.jpg&h=471759f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n片:<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/936508\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F936508&d=XUHW2qJizO2pFN7N4VPpEqtywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=5a26b166\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F936508&h=a43ad16f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/936508</a><br />\n<br />\n四名男女上周三（13日），佔用港珠澳大橋連接線拱北隧道西的應急車道，在馬路上蹦蹦跳<br />\n跳擺出各種姿勢在拍照，還從車上拿出幾盒飯盒，在橋上野餐起來，吃得津津有味，一名男子還把手裏沒吃完的食物丟入大海。<br />\n<br />\n據珠海交警周一（18日）發佈的一段影片可見，兩對男女陸續從一輛白色豐田下來，在應急車道上「旋轉跳躍」、「蹦蹦跳跳」擺各種姿勢拍照。之後，他們還從車內拿出幾份盒飯，用應急車道外的水泥護欄充當桌子吃飯。其中的一位年輕男子還直接把手裏沒吃完的點心扔向了大海。<br />\n<br />\n港珠澳大橋全長55千米，主橋全長約29.6千米，是連接香港大嶼山、澳門和廣東省珠海市的大型跨海通道。在這樣一個地方佔用緊急車道，並做出如此行為可能會帶來意想不到後果。珠海交警表示會將其違法記錄錄入系統，涉事的豐田車因非法佔用應急車道，將被處以罰款200元、記6分的處罰。"},{"pid":"82d62dc3789d9bbc823b9703880c156dd85a55f4","tid":1027852,"uid":74171,"like":356,"dislike":2,"score":354,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T05:37:52.000Z","msg":"一睇就知咩人"},{"pid":"bff23ec81b83d0af6aad33276025b38ededd9973","tid":1027852,"uid":232077,"like":9,"dislike":355,"score":-346,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T05:39:31.000Z","msg":"白衫要多圖唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/